      • getParameter

        public Value getParameter(java.lang.String name,
                          Value def)
        Gets a parameter from the incoming parameters from the endpoint. The default value type is checked against the type of the parameter as received from the endpoint. If the default value is null then then type is unchecked and a value of null can be returned.
        Parameters:
        name - Name of the parameter.
        def - Default value to return if the parameter doesn't exist.
        Returns:
        Returns a value.
